-- Berkshire’s Lubrizol Promotes Ghirardi, Kalhan in Home Care Jobs
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-08-21T13:09:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/berkshire-s-lubrizol-promotes-ghirardi-kalhan-in-home-care-jobs.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s Lubrizol
unit, the maker of engine additives and specialty chemicals,
promoted Dorina Ghirardi to global research and development
director for the personal and home care business.  Sanjay Kalhan was promoted to the new position of global
business director for home care and Arul Mathew was promoted to
business director of personal and home care for the Asia Pacific
region, according to a statement today from the unit of Omaha,
Nebraska-based Berkshire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in  New York  at 
